About 10 activists from the Congress’s youth wing entered the AI Summit venue in New Delhi on Friday and staged shirtless demonstration, shouting slogans against Prime Minister Narendra Modi over the India-US trade agreement (Image: X)

.snapShotAiSummery{ width: 100%; min-height: 52px; margin: 1.5rem 0; border-radius: 10px; background: linear-gradient(#fff, #fff) padding-box, linear-gradient(90.34deg, #53A633, #C0FCE8 45.3%, #1D92D6) border-box; border: 2px solid transparent; padding: 1.5rem; font: 400 1.2rem/1.5rem 'inter', sans-serif; color: #666;} .snapShotAiSummery .expandDetails .para ul, .snapShotAiSummery .expandDetails .para li{ list-style: disc; margin-left: 0px;} .snapShotAiSummery .contentWrap{ gap: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center;} .snapShotAiSummery .contentWrap .readMoreBtn{ margin-left: auto; width: 20px;} .snapShotAiSummery .readMoreBtn svg{ width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer;} .snapShotAiSummery .expandedIcon{ rotate: 180deg; margin-left: auto;} .expandDetails{ font: 400 1.2rem 'inter', sans-serif; color: #666; display: block; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.35s ease; width: 100%; display: block;} .expandDetails.open{ max-height: 500px;} .expandDetails .para{ display: block; font: 400 1.4rem/2rem 'inter', sans-serif; color: #000; margin: 1rem 0 0;} .expandDetails .feedbackSection{ display: flex; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem; border-top: 2px solid #D5D5D5; padding-top: 1em; gap:15px;} .expandDetails .iconList{ display: flex; align-items: center; gap:10px;} .expandDetails .iconList svg{ fill:none;} .readFullArticleLink{ margin-left: auto; cursor: pointer;} .snapShotAiSummery .expandDetails > .para br{ display: block;} .snapShotAiSummery button.like-btn, .snapShotAiSummery button.dislike-btn{ background: transparent; border: none;} .snapShotAiSummery button.like-btn.active svg, .snapShotAiSummery button.dislike-btn.active svg{ fill: #1D92D6; transform: scale(1.1);} .snapShotAiSummery .left-margin-amp{ margin-left: 10px;} @media all and (max-width:481px){ .snapShotAiSummery{ padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1rem; width: 100%;} .expandDetails .iconList{ gap: 6px;} .expandDetails .iconList a.readFullArticleLink{ margin-left: 4px;}}

Delhi Police claim Youth Congress protest inspired by Nepal's Gen Z

Police investigate funding, anti-Modi T-shirts at AI Summit

BJP condemns protest, calls it harmful to India's global image Did our AI summary help?

